reviewText: Great Godly songs that entertain and teach. We have several of the Miss Patty Cake dvds and my one year old daughter loves them!
My kids LOVE Miss Patty Cake!
Awesome video!!  My kids sing along to all of the wonderful Bible Songs!!
Product worked as advertised and am pleased with results.
PattyCakes does it again-- pretty much the same line up of her former Bible Song DVD with a few newer songs from the more recent Christmas album.

Miss Pattycake is great. I love teaching my preschoolers about Gods love for us and helping them engage in worship. This dvd teaches simple bible truths that the children can catch hold of. I will be buying more of her products.
Miss patticake teaches biblical truth in cute preschool songs...we enjoy her dvds
